Ahhh Yesss!<br><br>
Have to confess, Easy Ed, you are my idol! At least you are a good role model for us kids! Always did admire those chopper pilots.<br><br>
There two names on the Wall that belong to 2 special chopper pilots. One, Rand Merker, was a kid I went to high school with. The other name is Ralph Bigelow. I was able to ascertain his ID using resources on the net that listed casualties by date and province. His Loach was shot down as it lifted off from our perimeter carrying Lt John Kaugars (our FO) and Lt Neil Hayes on a recon of the area we were to head to that day. Can't describe the lost feeling and hopelessness, but I bet you know, Ed.<br><br>
Wish you could go back with me also, Ed. I will think of you, and all the others, when I get back to that little ville across the river from the Horseshoe. <br><br>
Peace to You my BOC,<br><br>
Tom
